==================== FIGMA ======================

Basic Figma shortcuts:
1. f: create a frame
2. R: draw a rectangle
3. R + shift: draw a square
4. R + shift + alt: draw a square in the center
5. Use Plugins

Layout
1. Use layout grid to put things precisely 
2. Auto layout: Select things, add auto layout and align them or double click the alignment to auto align 

Components and styles
-> Create your own components and styles to keep consistency

Prototypes
1. Click the prototype tab and add an interaction
